name: Traveler Prototype
description:
A throw back to arcade games, inspired by games like 1984,  Nanostray and Space Invaders. This is the final prototype from my team's coursework in  design mechanics 2.  while this project was made over a year ago and just an early prototype it is a bit of fun I though I would share.
